The paper deals with the problem of model selection, which is a fundamental problem in many areas of computer science and engineering. The paper introduces two measures of coherence and analyzes a specific algorithm for model selection. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Signal Processing (cs.SP), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
